      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **User Registration**: Allows new users to create an account.\n- **User Login**: Enables registered users to log in to their accounts.\n- **View Sweet Listing**: Displays all available sweets in a catalog format.\n- **Filter Sweets**: Allows users to filter sweets by category or other criteria.\n- **View Sweet Details**: Shows detailed information for a specific sweet.\n- **Purchase Sweets**: Enables users to add sweets to a cart and complete a purchase.\n- **Admin Add Sweet**: Allows administrators to add new sweets to the inventory.\n- **Admin Edit Sweet**: Allows administrators to modify existing sweet details.\n- **Admin Delete Sweet**: Allows administrators to remove sweets from the inventory.\n- **Admin Restock Sweet**: Allows administrators to update the stock levels of sweets.\n- **Search Sweets**: Enables users to search for specific sweets.",
